# Cross-BC (как в коде сейчас)

7 Domain BC: OrderFulfillment, ClientPortal, Company, Pricing, Equipment, Warehouse, Identity.  
Application-фасад: PublicSite (`GetPublicBootstrap`).

## Реализовано

- Domain Entity хранят только `*_id` на другие BC (без объектных ссылок)
- Eloquent models **без** cross-BC `belongsTo`/`hasMany` (кроме дочерних сущностей агрегата Order)
- Общая БД, монолит, FK в миграциях
- Cross-BC orchestration — только в `Application/{BC}/CommandHandler` или `ReadModel/*Builder`

## Cross-BC handlers (факт)

| Handler | BC | Порты других BC |
|---------|-----|-----------------|
| `CreateOrderHandler` | OrderFulfillment | `BranchRepositoryInterface` (Company) |
| `AddMaterialToOrderHandler` | OrderFulfillment | `WarehouseItemRepositoryInterface` |
| `LinkEquipmentToOrderHandler` | OrderFulfillment | `EquipmentRepositoryInterface` |
| `SubmitReviewHandler` | ClientPortal | `OrderRepositoryInterface` |
| `LinkGuestOrdersToClientHandler` | ClientPortal | `OrderRepositoryInterface` |
| `GetClientOrdersQueryHandler` | ClientPortal | `OrderRepositoryInterface` |
| `GetClientOrderDetailQueryHandler` | ClientPortal | `OrderRepositoryInterface` |
| `GenerateDocumentHandler` | OrderFulfillment | Company, Equipment, Identity, Warehouse (read model) |
| `GetEquipmentOrderHistoryQueryHandler` | Equipment | `OrderRepositoryInterface` |
| `GetPublicBootstrapQueryHandler` | PublicSite | Company + Pricing (delegation) |

## Read models across BC

- `OrderDocumentReadModelBuilder` — Order + Branch + SiteContent + Equipment + Master + WarehouseItem
- `PosOrderReadModelBuilder` — Order + Equipment + Master + WarehouseItem (имена материалов)

## Правило

Кросс-BC сценарии — только `Application/{BC}/CommandHandler` или `ReadModel/*Builder`, не Domain и не Eloquent-связи.
